# Title: Change the Fax Dll
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-07-17
# Level: high
# Description: Detect possible persistence using Fax DLL load when service restart
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1112
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_fax_dll_persistance.yml

TargetObject="*\\Software\\Microsoft\\Fax\\Device Providers\\*" TargetObject="*\\ImageName*" NOT Details="%systemroot%\\system32\\fxst30.dll"